    {
      "chinese": "第二點，是屬於家族的祝福儀式，如：「panqavic」謝產婆儀式，做餐點給產婆吃，他人都禁止食用。另一個是「matungaan」命名儀式，由家中長者來加喚「名靈」給新生嬰兒。還有一個是「anqaqavic」祝福禮，是謝姻親家族儀式。",
      "ab": "Maca taimipusan a, ituskun is maitatlumaq masumsum tuqumic is uvava’az, maupas itu panqavic tu sinsumsum, matas’is kakaunun na ispaka’us sicial is ququm iha’an tian, masamu ca duma’ bunun ma’us kakaunun dii. Maca ta’a ha, sinluc’as patingaan, na cias madaingaz ca luklac is ngaan ispatingaan is uva’az. Maizang ca ta’a ka ispaluc’as uava’az tupa’un tu anqaqavic, ala macuqais tuqumic is kitlumaq a sinsusumsum.",
      "order": "3",
