    {
      "chinese": "卓群布農族人視孩童的生命健康之後，才會舉行這個祝福禮。男方家族備妥禮品送給女方家族，將孩童帶到外婆跟前，應用「ngaan」菖浦傾注各種天恩的祝福。女方家族以乳豬或是其他的飼養物回贈，給幼兒帶回家。等飼養物長大之後，再邀請女方家族一起慶祝享用，以完成「anqaqavic」的嬰兒祝福儀式。",
      "ab": "Maca mananailang saduus uva’az tu maqtu’in malakackac miqumic, na asat luc’an masumsum is anqaqavic dii. Palasanuc is mama’az ca tatlumaq is bananzi’ na iscaiv is kitlumaq, adasun ca uva’az punha’an tantangaus is qudasnau’az cia, na kuci’aun ngaan patuqumic daidaz is Diqanin. Maca kitlumaqi’ a makucia auqaz cina duma’ a sinaipuk palacuqais, iscaiv is uava’az pa’adas mulumaq. Tudiip maca mindaingin ca sinaipuk dii ha, na muqnang muna’us kitlumaqi’ patan’ali, na pinaqtung is anqaqavic dii masumsum paluc’as uva’az.",
      "order": "4",
